"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.9.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.9.1</span> 标题：剃刀（razor）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מוֹרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：morah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:5\">JDG 13:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:17\">JDG 16:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:11\">1SA 1:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：תַּעַר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：ta‘ar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:5\">NUM 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num8:7\">NUM 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:4\">PSA 52:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:20\">ISA 7:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:23\">JER 36:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:1\">EZK 5:1</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0361_razor.jpg\" alt=\"古代剃须刀（埃及，公元前1550-1458年）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">古代剃须刀（埃及，公元前1550–1458年） (Metropolitan Museum of Art, Public domain, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>剃刀是一把非常锋利的刀，用来剃掉皮肤上的毛发。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:5\">NUM 6:5</a> 中（比较<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:5\">JDG 13:5</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:17\">JDG 16:17</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:11\">1SA 1:11</a> ），原文字面意为“任何剃刀都不可落在他的头上”一句可以译为：“他绝不能剪掉头发”，或“你一定不能剪掉或剃掉头发”（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 直译）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:23\">JER 36:23</a> 中提到的工具是一把小刀或剃刀，文士用它来削笔（参<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.7.3 笔 (pen)&lt;REALIA:1.7.3&gt;</a> ）。英文“penknife”（“削笔刀”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Revised Standard Version (1952)\">RSV</abbr> ）就源于这样的工具，尽管今天听到这个词的人会把它理解成一把折叠小刀。</p>\n<p>和许多物品一样，剃刀有时在圣经中用作比喻。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:4\">PSA 52:4</a> （《和》52:2）将舌头与锋利的剃刀相比拟。我们查阅的所有译本都保留了这个比喻。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:20\">ISA 7:20</a> 中，剃刀同样象征着亚述王的攻击。几乎所有的译本都在这段经文中保留了剃刀的比喻。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Good News Translation (1992)\">GNT</abbr> 只是间接提到这个比喻，英文直译为：“当那个时候来到，主会雇用一个从幼发拉底河那边来的理发师——就是亚述的王！——他会剃掉你的胡须和头发，还有你身体上的毛发。”</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
